"reviewcomment":"I had always heard Salad Stop was a great place for well..salads but I&#39;d never had a chance to go there myself until this week.<br><br>Everything sounded so delicious, and I knew I didn&#39;t want to go with the standard Hail Caesar since there were so many other innovative choices. I decided on the Oh Crab Lah! on a whole meal wrap which lured me with its Singapore Chili Crab Dressing. Not as spicy as I had hoped for but so flavourful and yummy! The wrap was massive and extremely filling. I didn&#39;t feel like I was eating just lettuce which tends to happen in poorly made Salads &amp; Wraps. They did an excellent job of tossing the ingredients together and making sure there was enough of everything.<br><br>This outlet at Suntec is on the smaller side, and they&#39;ve really packed in as many tables as physically possible. There is always a line out the door but it does move quite quickly. Recommended for a healthy, grab and go lunch on a busy work day!",
